body:
This thread is to show what places every team came in, in projection redemption (Record is ONLY for qualifier rounds)
http://avicus.challonge.com/ProjectRedemption/groups

1. Team Allah (4-1)
2. Sagrevyum (4-1)
3. ApoLLo (5-0)
4. Cennet (5-0)
5. Team Rocket (3-2)
6. Cronus (2-3)
7. Cacalmarin (2-3)
8. Jalapenos (2-3)
9. Spacedeepers (2-3)
10. HOME (1-4)
11. Twix (0-5)
12. labradoodles (0-5) [DQ]

1. Who was the biggest shock in this tournament? For me, it was sagrevyum.
2. Which match was the biggest upset? Jalapenos beating cronus.
